subject: YOUR ATM CARD PACKAGE IS READY NOW GET BACK TO ME
body:

Note your mail is well received. I got a message from FedEx delivery

said the International Airport in your state required an insurance coverage
certificate before the package moved to your address. Can you provide the
insurance coverage certificate? It costs $25 to obtain it here.

subject: Re: YOUR ATM CARD PACKAGE IS READY NOW GET BACK TO ME
body:
Hello Mr. Peter Iwu,

Thank you for your email and the information provided. It's interesting to hear about the insurance coverage requirement from the airport in my state. I wasn't aware of this before.

Could you please provide more details about this insurance coverage? What exactly does it cover and how does it work? Also, could you let me know how much it costs?

I'm also curious about the tracking number you mentioned. Could you please share that with me so I can track the package?

Looking forward to hearing from you soon.

Best regards.

Best wishes,
Alice
